Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.03,otherstuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fnRage Italic LET\fs36\pos(449,184)}Takara Miyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.03,otherstuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnRage Italic LET\fs36\be1\pos(222,256)}Hiiragi Tsukasa
